00:56:47.420 --> 00:56:50.290 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now it’s time for our video postcard.

00:56:50.290 --> 00:56:54.994 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s visit our brothers and sisters
in Madagascar.

00:56:54.994 --> 00:56:58.665 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Lying off the east coast of Africa,

00:56:58.665 --> 00:57:02.702 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Madagascar is the fourth largest island
in the world.

00:57:02.702 --> 00:57:07.240 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Its climate and diverse terrain make it

00:57:07.240 --> 00:57:12.112 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a sanctuary for an amazing variety
of plants and animals.

00:57:13.179 --> 00:57:15.148 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The baobab tree is known

00:57:15.148 --> 00:57:17.717 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
for its barrel-shaped trunk

00:57:17.717 --> 00:57:20.420 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and extraordinary longevity.

00:57:20.420 --> 00:57:22.455 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There are nine species

00:57:22.455 --> 00:57:25.291 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of baobab in the world.

00:57:25.291 --> 00:57:29.162 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Six can be found only in Madagascar.

00:57:29.162 --> 00:57:32.132 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
About 40 different species

00:57:32.132 --> 00:57:34.167 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of lemur live here.

00:57:34.167 --> 00:57:38.037 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Among them is the ring-tailed lemur,

00:57:38.037 --> 00:57:42.075 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and this one is called Coquerel’s sifaka.

00:57:42.075 --> 00:57:45.378 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Rice fields dot many parts of the country.

00:57:45.378 --> 00:57:49.315 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Rice is the staple food
of the Malagasy people.

00:57:51.251 --> 00:57:55.288 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Antsirabe is Madagascar’s third largest city

00:57:55.288 --> 00:57:58.825 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and home to 34 congregations.

00:57:58.825 --> 00:58:03.129 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Since few in Madagascar have running water,

00:58:03.129 --> 00:58:06.132 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
many people can be contacted
while they do their laundry

00:58:06.132 --> 00:58:08.334 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in rivers and lakes.

00:58:08.334 --> 00:58:11.204 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Let’s visit Tanambao Sahafony,

00:58:11.204 --> 00:58:16.075 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
a remote community on the southeastern coast.

00:58:16.075 --> 00:58:20.346 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Our brothers share the good news
despite frequent rain showers

00:58:20.346 --> 00:58:24.551 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the great distances
they have to walk between villages.

00:58:26.653 --> 00:58:31.124 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Response to the Kingdom message is strong,
and many ask for a Bible study.

00:58:32.192 --> 00:58:36.162 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Here, two sisters are conducting a study

00:58:36.162 --> 00:58:38.464 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
while others wait their turn.

00:58:38.464 --> 00:58:40.500 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Interested ones

00:58:40.500 --> 00:58:43.670 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
walk up to 16 kilometers, or about 10 miles,

00:58:43.670 --> 00:58:46.506 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
every week to attend meetings.

00:58:46.506 --> 00:58:50.276 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The village has no electricity.

00:58:50.276 --> 00:58:53.546 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So to download big video files

00:58:53.546 --> 00:58:55.648 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
such as convention videos,

00:58:55.648 --> 00:59:00.253 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
this elder and other brothers
travel 12 hours,

00:59:00.253 --> 00:59:02.822 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
mainly by boat, to the nearest town.

00:59:05.024 --> 00:59:07.694 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There are 32 publishers in the congregation,

00:59:07.694 --> 00:59:11.264 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but on average, 150 people

00:59:11.264 --> 00:59:15.101 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
attend weekend meetings
—40 percent of them children.

00:59:17.303 --> 00:59:20.607 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
